ts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158859/', '', 'Thiopental, Ethchlorvynol, Dichloralphenazone, Ephedrine, Tropicamide, Phenylephrine, Rolapitant', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
